Today is National Teacher Appreciation Day 2017, and we are taking the opportunity to honor just a few of the many outstanding teachers at The Grosse Pointe Academy. Below we have republished a collection of articles that were culled primarily from interviews over the past several years with a number of GPAs esteemed faculty members.

There are more articles about Academy teachers posted to the GPA website. Take a stroll through the site and find out even more about why Academyteachers are so dedicated to the education and well-being of our students.

